{
  "stem": "13382.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother told me-- to save me from communism, she asked me to leave that area and go to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here I am.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, you know, I haven't got any identification.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want to get a flat to live in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't get anything, because I have no papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what is your name?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I told them my name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My name is [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Lukasz ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Janosz. ?] I was born in Dombagyhaz, where my sister-- everything was sort of a copy, except the name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said I was born in 1926, because it's no point to have 1925, because I called into the army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I might as well I change my birth year as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And being [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lukasz ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Janosz, ?] John Lowy-- you know, everything sort of-- I made it as sort of easy and born there, to remember these things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have a perfect, legal identification card.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Lukasz ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Janosz. ?] And I went and I asked for a-- as a refugee, a place to live.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was allocated part of a flat unit, in-- not far from-- from the-- from the Eastern Railway station, I think [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Zuglo ?] utca or something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one part of this was occupied by quite a high position officer in the-- in the railway, with a wife and a-- and a little kid.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one room, or one part, was mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he used the kitchen and everything was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I was a real Gentile with-- and that flat was sometimes belonged to Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You see, when Jewish people went out of these areas, so they're allocating the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I was one now allocated as a Gentile.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
